# Hello World Frontend

A simple, elegant Hello World frontend project built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- 🎨 Beautiful gradient background with glassmorphism design
- ✨ Interactive buttons for color change and animations
- 📱 Responsive design
- ⚡ Fast development server with Vite

## Quick Start

### Option 1: Simple HTML File
Simply open `index.html` in your web browser.

### Option 2: Development Server (Recommended)
```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

Then open http://localhost:4173 in your browser.

## Project Structure

```
hello-world-frontend/
├── index.html          # Main HTML file
├── style.css           # Styles and animations
├── script.js           # Interactive functionality
├── package.json        # Project configuration
└── README.md           # This file
```

## Available Scripts

- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run preview` - Preview production build

## Customization

- Modify colors in `style.css`
- Add new interactions in `script.js`
- Update content in `index.html`

## Browser Support

Works in all modern browsers including:
- Chrome 60+
- Firefox 55+
- Safari 12+
- Edge 79+
```endfile

